### 8.5 Smoothness Metrics in Rehabilitation

#### Paper 12: SPARC (Balasubramanian et al., 2012/2015)
- **Citation**: Balasubramanian, S. et al. (2012). "A robust and sensitive metric for quantifying movement smoothness." *IEEE Trans. Biomed. Eng.*, 59(8), 2126-2136.
- **GitHub**: https://github.com/siva82kb/SPARC
- **Overlap**: Contribution 5 (SPARC smoothness metric)
- **Methods**: Spectral Arc Length — frequency-domain smoothness metric
- **Results**: 1000+ citations; amplitude/duration invariant; gold standard
- **Limitations**: Metric only, not a complete system
- **Compare on**: SPARC correlation with clinical scores

